  "short_description": "7-inch multi-touch display, 1 Gbps RJ45 port, Bluetooth 4.2, 802.3af PoE, IP65 rated, -30°C to 60°C operating temperature",
  "description": "The Ubiquiti UniFi Access G3 Intercom (UA-G3-Intercom) is equipped with a high-definition camera that delivers clear video feeds, ensuring precise identification of individuals at entry points. Complementing the camera is a 7-inch capacitive multi-touch LCD with a resolution of 1024 x 600 pixels, offering an intuitive interface for users to interact with the system. The display achieves a maximum luminance of 1000 nits, ensuring visibility even in brightly lit environments. This combination of high-resolution video and responsive touchscreen enhances user experience and security management at access points.",
  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Versatile Access Methods",
      "text": "The UA-G3-Intercom supports multiple authentication methods, including NFC card access, PIN codes, and mobile credentials via the UniFi Identity mobile app. It is compatible with various NFC technologies such as ISO/IEC 14443A/B, 15693, and 18092 (Ecma 340), accommodating MIFARE Classic, MIFARE DESFIRE, and Sony FeliCa standards. This versatility allows for seamless integration into existing access control systems. Additionally, the device features a built-in doorbell function and can pair with multiple UniFi Intercom Viewers, facilitating remote access control and communication."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Robust Construction",
      "text": "Designed for both indoor and outdoor installations, the UA-G3-Intercom boasts an IP65-rated enclosure, providing protection against dust and water ingress. The device operates reliably within a temperature range of -30°C to 60°C, making it suitable for different environmental conditions. Constructed with an aluminum alloy and UV-stabilized polycarbonate housing, it offers durability and resistance to environmental wear, ensuring long-term performance. Its impact-resistant structure also helps safeguard critical components from tampering or accidental damage. These design features make it ideal for high-traffic entryways, gated perimeters, and exposed commercial entrances where durability is essential."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Connectivity and Power",
      "text": "The UA-G3-Intercom features a Gigabit Ethernet RJ45 port for high-speed network connectivity and supports Power over Ethernet (PoE) with a 48V DC input, simplifying installation by combining power and data transmission over a single cable. The device's maximum power consumption is 13W, promoting energy efficiency and minimizing infrastructure costs. In addition to PoE support, the intercom’s efficient network interface ensures low-latency communication, crucial for real-time video and audio transmissions. Compliance with UL 294 and CAN/ULC-60839-11-1 standards underscores its adherence to stringent safety and performance criteria, making it a reliable choice for secure access control implementations."
    }
  ],
